ems","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.heuristicallyExtractSimpTheorems","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L100-L111","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.heuristicallyExtractSimpTheoremsCore","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.heuristicallyExtractSimpTheoremsCore","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L94-L98","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.isEqnLemma?","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.isEqnLemma?","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L84-L92","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.constToSimpDeclMap","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.constToSimpDeclMap","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L75-L77","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.elements","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.elements","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L69-L73","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.trieElements","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.trieElements","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L65-L66","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.isSimpTheorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.isSimpTheorem","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Simp.lean#L58-L63","name":"Mathlib.T